{"tid":786084,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「最能駕馭紅唇的女偶像」BEST7！每個人的風格都不同...","createTime":"2018-08-19T16:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T05:53:06.000Z","uid":51412,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"584cbfbca020d7774a660ab7a60f64f02c869ba5","tid":786084,"uid":51412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"「最能駕馭紅唇的女偶像」BEST7！每個人的風格都不同...性感致命VS高冷霸氣，你愛哪<br />\n一種？<br />\n<br />\n雖然風格不同，但她們真的都很適合紅唇阿！<br />\n<br />\n紅唇是一個看似普通卻不容易被駕馭的唇色，以下幾位是提到紅唇時，大部分的人會想到<br />\n的女偶像，一起來看看吧！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/d6Dal6n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fd6Dal6n.png&h=24d9ff0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n# LE<br />\n經常以紅唇現身的霸氣rapper LE，女王氣場一出現就能吸引眾人目光！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ySclkVC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FySclkVC.png&h=9dbc485e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n# 娜璉<br />\n紅花+紅洋裝+紅唇三種SET一次完成！就像人魚公主愛麗兒一樣呢~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HpDgne2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHpDgne2.png&h=7b36d9c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n# Joy<br />\n黑髮Joy配上紅唇真的美到不行！每次看都會被九妹驚艷到阿~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hQ4zeFq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhQ4zeFq.png&h=7d1cbbc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n# 華莎<br />\n有著相較於年齡較成熟的外表，塗上紅唇更是性感指數加倍！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MlIheUU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMlIheUU.png&h=d080cf2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n# 泫雅<br />\n紅唇的終結者當然不能少了泫雅！美麗的紅唇基本上就是泫雅的標誌阿~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IJUXqvI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIJUXqvI.png&h=45e284e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n# SUNMI<br />\nSUNMI對紅唇的消化力絕對是無庸置疑，在她身上紅唇真的是一個必殺武器！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oAcvqsu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FoAcvqsu.png&h=20863c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n# 度延<br />\n曾被韓媒提到跟SUNMI的紅唇值得一比，精緻的五官配上紅唇立刻變身女神！<br />\n<br />\n這幾位的紅唇真的都超級美麗，還有哪位女偶像的紅唇也不能錯過呢？快點留言跟大家分<br />\n享吧！"},{"pid":"bf39963ecd31a620186b41e88f5ab6c408812f72","tid":786084,"uid":2546,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:48:48.000Z","msg":"其實tiffany都幾襯紅唇"},{"pid":"50ed37054c371278c0e6dda1b92e4c8336f871bb","tid":786084,"uid":18456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:26:00.000Z","msg":"我的確世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901719ea5cf8a1101b1ac1b02c7fcd670dd79058","tid":786084,"uid":51412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T12:45:17.000Z","msg":"PUS"},{"pid":"cb2bef290f81d2a16215d7a466baa796a2da406d","tid":786084,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"50ed37054c371278c0e6dda1b92e4c8336f871bb","tid":786084,"uid":18456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:26:00.000Z","msg":"我的確世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:07:19.000Z","msg":"你呢幾年的確靚到痴左線"},{"pid":"9ec65bba36168bd628d7d1be4be5434838d03121","tid":786084,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb2bef290f81d2a16215d7a466baa796a2da406d","tid":786084,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"50ed37054c371278c0e6dda1b92e4c8336f871bb","tid":786084,"uid":18456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:26:00.000Z","msg":"我的確世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:07:19.000Z","msg":"你呢幾年的確靚到痴左線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T14:04:36.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"f5e504833ec590ecf373e0b4a707d72b90cb1c05","tid":786084,"uid":18456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T14:53:07.000Z","msg":"上面兩位ching真識貨<img 